HEADWORD: Palmae
<hw>Palmae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural family of chiefly
tropical trees and shrubs; same as <er>Palmaceae</er>; coextensive with
the order <ord>Palmales</ord>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Palmae</fam>, <fam>Palmaceae</fam>,
<fam>Arecaceae</fam>, family <fam>Arecaceae</fam>, palm
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
